\begin_layout Enumerate
球外空间的格林函数，设球外电荷位置为
\begin_inset Formula $R^{\prime}=\sqrt{x^{\prime2}+y^{\prime2}+z^{\prime2}}$
\end_inset

,
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
G\left(\sbf x,\sbf x^{\prime}\right)=\frac{1}{4\pi\varepsilon_{0}}\left[\frac{1}{\sqrt{R^{2}+R^{\prime2}-2RR^{\prime}\cos\alpha}}-\frac{1}{\sqrt{\left(\frac{RR^{\prime}}{R_{0}}\right)^{2}+R_{0}^{2}-2RR^{\prime}\cos\alpha}}\right]
\]

\end_inset

其中
\begin_inset Formula $\cos\alpha=\cos\theta\cos\theta^{\prime}+\sin\theta\sin\theta^{\prime}\cos\left(\phi-\phi^{\prime}\right)$
\end_inset

，是场点和原点矢径的夹角，
\begin_inset Formula $R_{0}$
